#COVID19 in Europe: French drugmaker #Sanofi has said it will bottle and package 125 million doses of the coronavirus vaccine developed by its rivals Pfizer BioNTech. Meanwhile, AstraZeneca denies EU accusations it has failed its #vaccine delivery targets.
